# Gracewood Acres — redirect rules for Netlify
# Format:  /old-path   /new-path   301
# 301 = permanent redirect (tells Google the page moved for good).
#
# These forward common old Wix URLs to the new pages so anyone with an
# old bookmark or link still lands somewhere useful instead of a 404.
# Add or edit lines as needed — one rule per line.

